Package: EsoralPrint
Type: Package
Title: EsoralPrint: Platform-Agnostic Quantification for Molecular Interception of Oral and Esophageal Malignancies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Homing", "Lai", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Implements a scalable, objective, platform-independent, and quantitative measure of 
    the molecular-morphological gap that complements traditional histological grading in OSCC and ESCC.
    It operates on a true single-sample basis, with no need for batch correction, 
    centralized calibration protocols, or strict adherence to inter-sample quality controls. 
